  "detailed_description": "Its a physics puzzle game.You can draw any shape you want and they are all followed by physics rules when you draw your first line or polygon.<br />\r\nYour goal is to use this physics line or polygon to push the ball to the same color cup.<br />\r\nWhen the physics ball drop into the correct color cup,the level is finished!<br />\r\nIts a nice brain-training game.Hope you can learn physics from the game.<br />\r\nHave fun.More levels is coming!",
